---
@META
dir: skillsPraut/public
updated: 2026-04-15
subdirs: 2 (fonts/, logo/)
stack: static assets (SVG, PNG, TTF/WOFF)

@EXPORTS
logo/brain-mark.svg — Praut brain puzzle mark (isolated)
logo/logopraut.svg — full logo + wordmark
logo/praut.svg — alt logo variant
logo/praut-logo.png — raster logo
logo/praut-large.png — large raster variant
logo/icon-zapisovatel-{256,1024}.png — "zapisovatel" (notetaker) app icon
fonts/phosphor/{thin,light,regular,bold,fill,duotone}/ — 6 Phosphor icon font variants (binary)

@PROCESSES
asset-loading: Remotion `staticFile(path)` → resolves against public/ → URL for <Img>/<Video>
font-loading: loadPhosphorFont.ts → loadFont() per weight → registers as Phosphor-{Weight}

@DEPENDENCIES
referenced-by: components/frame/BrainMark.tsx (logopraut.svg) | components/frame/BrandLogo.tsx | components/icons/loadPhosphorFont.ts | renders (for YouTube thumbnails)

@STANDARDS
- All static assets served via Remotion staticFile() helper
- Logo variants: brain-mark (icon only) | full (mark + wordmark) | text-only
- Phosphor font files follow phosphor-icons v2 naming convention
- No user-uploaded content — only branded assets

@WARNINGS
- Phosphor font binaries are large; commit only essential weights
- logo/icon-zapisovatel-*.png referenced for secondary app/channel; not EP01 mainline
